data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This single-story residence is thoughtfully designed to provide comfort and convenience. As you enter, you'll be greeted by a spacious living area with high ceilings, allowing for an airy and open atmosphere. The kitchen seamlessly connects to the living room, creating a perfect space for entertaining and spending quality time with loved ones.The home boasts four bedrooms,two and half bathrooms providing ample space for relaxation and privacy. The master bedroom features a luxurious touch with a walk-in closet, ensuring you have plenty of storage space for your belongings. The kitchen is a focal point of this home, showcasing a stunning Resina Expoxy island that serves as a gathering place for family and friends. The vinyl flooring throughout the home not only adds a touch of elegance but is also easy to maintain, perfect for a busy lifestyle.Natural light floods the rooms, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. Additionally, the two-car garage provides secure parking and extra storage space.This home encompasses the perfect combination of practicality and style, offering a comfortable and modern living experience. Ceiling Fan in leaving room in not included.
